OL,6,FA fire which destroyed a leisure
OL,7,Fcentre is being treated as
OL,8,F'suspicious'.
OL,10,FThe blaze broke out at , Salford, just
OL,11,Fbefore 3am on Friday 10 May.
OL,13,FEight fire engines and specialist
OL,14,Fappliances were used to tackle the
OL,15,Fblaze. Since the incident, no arrests
OL,16,For injuries have been reported.
OL,18,FThe centre was due to reopen in June
OL,19,F2024 after it received significant
OL,20,Finvestment for a new state of the art
OL,21,Fgym.
