OL,6,FDiscussions are now taking place
OL,7,Fbetween Salford City Council and
OL,8,FSalford Community Leisure to work out
OL,9,Fthe future of the site, including the
OL,10,Fpossibility of a rebuild.
OL,12,F(GMP) said: "Investigators are
OL,13,Festablishing the exact cause of the
OL,14,Ffire and work is ongoing to piece
OL,15,Ftogether the timeline of events.
OL,17,F"The incident is currently being
OL,18,Ftreated as suspicious, and officers
OL,19,Fare keen for anyone with any
OL,20,Finformation that could help the
OL,21,Finvestigation to come forward."
