OL,6,FClarendon Leisure Centre had been
OL,7,Fpreviously earmarked for possible
OL,8,Fclosure - to be replaced by one of
OL,9,Fseveral new centres planned for the
OL,10,Fcity.
OL,12,FHowever those plans were halted in
OL,13,Frecent years as the economy dipped.
