OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Karl Perry, from
OL,7,FGMP's Salford district, said:
OL,8,F"Incidents such as the one we saw on
OL,9,FFriday morning can be both upsetting
OL,10,Fand shocking ` but I want local people
OL,11,Fto know that we are utilising all
OL,12,Flines of enquiry as we look to
OL,13,Fdiscover what triggered this awful
OL,14,Ffire.
