OL,6,FHe said comments they have received
OL,7,Fsince the fire "show how important
OL,8,Fthis venue was for the community, with
OL,9,Fso many people sharing such fond
OL,10,Fmemories".
OL,12,FAll staff working at Clarendon have
OL,13,Fbeen 'redeployed' to its other centres
OL,14,Fand services in Salford.
